Cell["\<\
Notes for next meeting

- Went through papers using ctrl F and also put them through, couldnt see \
anything to help with 1/u^3
- added in the epsilon to fix the issue, worked and got to the centre, \
although abruptly, maybe I can just turn off the drag if it becomes less \
important or something
- looked at PBH coming from infinity and got that setup as in paper, although \
issue with singularity persisted\
\>", "Text",
